On Friday morning Eskom announced that it had decided to re-appoint Brian Molefe as its CEO. JOHANNESBURG - Business Leadership SA Chair Jabu Mabuza says Brian Molefe's reinstatement as Eskom CEO is the most bizarre, most diabolical decision he s ever heard.On Friday morning Eskom announced that it had decided to re-appoint Molefe as its CEO.Molefe resigned last year after the Public Protector's state capture report showed that he had been in constant contact with the Gupta family during a deal involving a coal mine that supplies Eskom.Mabuza said: &quot;Molefe reinstatement is an insult to the citizens of this country, the whole board needs to be expelled.&quot;He wants Eskom s entire board to go That whole board need to be expelled.&quot;